title: Leading Women with Page Executive | Alexandra Cerruti, Managing Director at Design Bridge
content: As part of our Leading Women series, we want to highlight the professional challenges and career aspirations of the women we work with here in Asia Pacific. In this story, we speak to Alexandra Cerruti about the women that have inspired her professional career, what keeps her motivated and engaged at work, as well as how the company at large celebrates diversity on a day-to-day basis.
